<exploration xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xml:id="PA-poly-rational-features">

	<statement>
		<p>
			Considera la función racional <m>r(x) = \frac{x^2 - 1}{x^2 - 3x - 4}</m>, y sea <m>p(x) = x^2 - 1</m> (el numerador de <m>r(x)</m>) y <m>q(x) = x^2 - 3x - 4</m> (el denominador de <m>r(x)</m>).
		</p>

<!--
		<figure xml:id="F-rational-features-hole-1">
